    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, affordable ride that gets the job done? This car offers dependable transportation at a great value price! It shows its age with some visible wear on the interior and exterior \u2014 think scuffs, minor blemishes, and the kind of character that comes with regular use \u2014 but it runs and drives, making it a practical choice for a budget-conscious buyer. A little TLC could go a long way here, and you're getting honest value for your dollar!",
