      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, no-nonsense daily driver? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it's a solid, functional vehicle that gets you where you need to go without breaking the bank! You'll notice some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections inside and out, as you'd expect from a well-used car, but mechanically it's a dependable everyday ride. If you're after reliable transportation at a wallet-friendly price, this one is worth a look!",
      "price": 21000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition at an honest price of $6,500, and full transparency is important here. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect multiple deep scratches, noticeable dents, faded or peeling paint, and likely some rust or corrosion in various areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it may run, but it is not in reliable daily-driver condition and will need repairs before it can be counted on. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or interested in parts. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just an honest assessment of a car that has seen better days.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, and buyers should have realistic expectations before inquiring. The exterior shows significant wear, including noticeable rust, dents, and paint deterioration that goes beyond cosmetic concerns. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard components, and general neglect throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will likely require substantial repairs \u2014 it may not be fully reliable for daily driving in its current state. This listing is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle, someone looking for parts, or a mechanically skilled individual who can invest the time and money to bring it back to working order. What you see is what you get, and we want you to go in with full knowledge of the car's condition.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition, and that is a fully honest and accurate representation \u2014 this car is as close to flawless as you will find on the used market. The exterior is stunning: the paint is deep, glossy, and free of scratches, chips, swirl marks, or fading \u2014 it looks as though it just rolled off a showroom floor. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, all trim pieces are intact and pristine, and the glass is clear with no chips or cracks. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 seats, carpets, headliner, and all surfaces show virtually no wear whatsoever. Every button, knob, screen, and feature functions exactly as intended, with no warning lights, electrical gremlins, or mechanical issues to report. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs smoothly; all fluids are fresh, and the vehicle has been meticulously maintained with service records to back it up. Tires have excellent tread remaining and are evenly worn. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that truly feels new \u2014 ideal for a buyer who wants the best without paying new-car prices.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly & Ready for a New Owner \u2014 A No-Frills Fixer at an Honest Price! \ud83d\udd27 This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it's seen better days and shows its age both inside and out, with visible wear, cosmetic imperfections, and mechanical issues that will need attention. That said, it still has real value as an affordable entry-level ride or a project car for the handy buyer! If you're looking for the most budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel and don't mind rolling up your sleeves, this could be your opportunity. Priced to reflect its true condition \u2014 no surprises, just straightforward savings! \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f",
      "price": 6500.0,
